Package algonquin.cst2335.finalandroidgroupproject

Class Flight

java.lang.Object
algonquin.cst2335.finalandroidgroupproject.Flight
public class Flight extends Object
Represents a flight entity in the Flight Tracker application. This class provides detailed information about a specific flight, including details about departure, arrival, terminal, gate, delay, and more.
